Description_lang: Torq's suit amplifies the electrical charges generated within $s2 yards. Until the next $@spellname465833, an electric charge courses through players that enter into range, inflicting $474159s3 Nature damage every $474159t3 sec. Additionally, while in range, the charge grows when the target moves and depletes when they are stationary. At max charge, it erupts into a $@spellname473983.
AuraDescription_lang: $474159s3 Nature damage inflicted every $474159t3 sec. Moving increases charge, staying still reduces it. Reaching max charge triggers a $@spellname473983.
